body:
Hey, so I have idiot friends...

They told me over discord, &quot;Everytime I get a kill, say &#039;%%%% %%%%&#039; okay?&quot;
me: &quot;Wait, isn&#039;t that like, slang for an asian/foreigner?&quot;
them: &quot;No no, it&#039;s fine you&#039;re good!&quot;
they got 2 kills in a row so I complied (idiot me am I right), so I said it twice...

Then I got banned... for 14 days... I was bait banned. We didn&#039;t think twice about, so that&#039;s on us. But reguardless, I wasn&#039;t calling anyone that, I&#039;m a good player (just reached honor lvl 3 checkpoint 1 too Q_Q and they fucking ruined it for me) , I&#039;ve never been chat restricted/banned ever, nor have I had anything but afk&#039;s ever in my league &quot;career&quot;.

In the end, I do regret not double checking their &quot;facts&quot; (and playing with them &gt;_&gt;), and will double check if I have any concerns about such... But overall I&#039;m a good player to play with, I get plenty of honors, and I hate to see that get murdered by a stupid prank. I can download the entire replay. Saying racist slurs and stuff like that is not who I am, I might swear, but never racist. 

I will also be putting in a ticket about this. Thank you and hopefully I can play again shortly...
